text.content: I am writing to formally notify you of my intent to terminate the lease for the property located at
(Rental Property Address). This letter serves as (number of days) days' notice as required by our
My move-out date will be (Your Intended Move-Out Date), which aligns with the end of the notice
period. I will ensure the property is left in clean and good condition, and I am happy to schedule
a walk-through inspection at your convenience.
Please let me know the steps and timeline for returning the security deposit. You may contact
me at (Phone Number) or (Email Address) if further information is needed.
Thank you for the opportunity to rent your property. I appreciate your attention and cooperation
in making this a smooth transition.
